%N A395337 Numbers that are Ramanujan's largely composite numbers (A067128) but not highly abundant numbers (A002093).
%C A395337 Not all Ramanujan's largely composite numbers are highly abundant numbers. This sequence shows the exceptions.
%e A395337 672 is in this sequence because 672 is a largely composite number, since 672 has 24 divisors and no number from 1 and 671 has more than 24 divisors; and 672 is not a highly abundant number, because sigma(660) = 2016 equals sigma(672) = 2016.
